<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Zanahary tsy mba tia FFPM28</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zanahary tsy mba tia
 Ny fahaverezanao
 Izy, Rainao be fitia,
 Tsy mba mahafoy anao.
 Ny famoizam-po ario,
 Fa Jesosy itokio,
 Mba hatoninao anio
 Ilay be fahasoavana !

[V2]
 Izy dia nitady ela,
 Vao nahita anao izao ;
 Mifalia, tsy ho ela
 Dia hody hianao.
 He, ry ondry saiky very,
 Ory, osa, feno fery,
 Ny Mpamonjy manan-kery
 Hahasitrana anao !

[V3]
 Ny ao an-danitra mifaly,
 Raha misy miova fo,
 Ary any ny anjely
 Miramirana avokoa.
 Fo marary dia tsaboiny,
 Ahiahim-po vonoiny,
 Fiadanana lazainy ;
 Sambatra isika re !</lyrics>
<hymn_number>28</hymn_number>
<author>L.M. Lindeman</author>
</song>